quran[6]{c,v,t,f}:
  7,88,"Àwọn àgbààgbà tó ṣègbéraga nínú ìjọ rẹ̀ wí pé: “Dájúdájú a máa lé ìwọ Ṣu‘aeb àti àwọn tó gbàgbọ́ pẹ̀lú rẹ jáde kúrò nínú ìlú wa tàbí kí ẹ padà sínú ẹ̀sìn wa.” (Ṣu‘aeb) sọ pé: “Ṣé (ẹ máa dá wa padà sínú ìbọ̀rìṣà) tó sì jẹ́ pé ẹ̀mí wa kọ̀ ọ́?”"
  7,89,"Dájúdájú a ti dá àdápa irọ́ mọ́ Allāhu tí a bá fi lè padà sínú ẹ̀sìn yín lẹ́yìn ìgbà tí Allāhu ti yọ wá kúrò nínú rẹ̀. Àti pé kò lẹ́tọ̀ọ́ fún wa láti padà sínú rẹ̀ àfi tí Allāhu Olúwa wa bá fẹ́. Olúwa wa fi ìmọ̀ rọkiriká gbogbo n̄ǹkan. Allāhu l’a gbáralé. Olúwa wa, ṣe ìdájọ́ láààrin àwa àti ìjọ wa pẹ̀lú òdodo, Ìwọ sì lóore jùlọ nínú àwọn olùdájọ́.”"
  7,90,"Àwọn àgbààgbà tó ṣàì gbàgbọ́ nínú ìjọ rẹ̀ wí pé: “Dájúdájú tí ẹ̀yin bá tẹ̀lé Ṣu‘aeb, nígbà náà ẹ̀yin ti di ẹni òfò nìyẹn.”"
  8,22,"Dájúdájú ẹ̀dá abẹ̀mí tó burú jùlọ ní ọ̀dọ̀ Allāhu ni àwọn adití, ayaya tí kò ṣe làákàyè."
  8,23,"Tí ó bá jẹ́ pé Allāhu mọ oore kan lára wọn ni, ìbá jẹ́ kí wọ́n gbọ́. Tí (Allāhu) bá sì fún wọn gbọ́ ni, dájúdájú wọn máa pẹ̀yìn dà, wọn yó sì máa gbúnrí."
  8,24,"Ẹ̀yin tí ẹ gbàgbọ́ ní òdodo, ẹ jẹ́pè ti Allāhu àti ti Òjíṣẹ́ nígbà tí ó bá pè yín síbi n̄ǹkan tí ó máa mu yín ṣẹ̀mí. Kí ẹ sì mọ̀ pé dájúdájú Allāhu ń ṣèdíwọ́ láààrin ènìyàn àti ọkàn rẹ̀. Dájúdájú ọ̀dọ̀ Rẹ̀ sì ni wọ́n máa ko yín jọ sí."